@node NPI Interface Conformance
@section NPI Interface Conformance
@cindex NPI interface conformance

The @cite{@value{PACKAGE_TITLE}} drivers conform to the @cite{Network Provider Interface (NPI)
Revision 2.0.0} as released by @cite{UNIX International}.  A copy of the original document is
available from @uref{http://www.openss7.org/docs/npi.pdf, The OpenSS7 Project Website}.
A reprint of the document specifying this version of the protocol is available as part of the
@samp{strxns} package available on line in @uref{http://www.openss7.org/specs/npi.pdf, PDF format},
or also in simple @uref{http://www.openss7.org/specs/npi.html, HTML format}.

